snippet: United Parcel Service and FedEx, the two major package delivery companies, have benefited as free shipping and returns have become more common among online retailers.
abstract: United Parcel Service and FedEx see benefit to trend of free shipping and returns among online retailers, with both delivery services showing boost in their number of shipments and increases to their bottom lines.
lead_paragraph: United Parcel Service and FedEx, the two major package delivery companies, have benefited as free shipping and returns have become more common among online retailers.

headline.seo: Record Online Retail Sales Buoy U.P.S. and FedEx
headline.main: Online Sales Buoy U.P.S. And FedEx
